    "claim": "`redeemCollateral()` trusts the authorized redemption handler to have retired `_amount` debt tokens elsewhere, but it reduces `totalBorrow` and transfers collateral based only on `msg.sender == redemptionHandler`. Likewise, `liquidate()` clears the borrower through `_repay(..., address(0), ...)` and releases collateral before merely asking the liquidation handler to process the debt externally. The pair itself never verifies that the corresponding stablecoin burn actually happened.",
